{"tid":344024,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有冇諗過到如果見到鬼，諗下之後點？","createTime":"2017-08-02T03:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T04:33:12.000Z","uid":6443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"32fb2281c7d35fd7bc9deb850b4959013c4d7d09","tid":344024,"uid":6443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:10:39.000Z","msg":"見有巴打開post講如果比鬼殺左之後好尷尬<br />\n<br />\n我自己有諗過類似既野想分享下<br />\n<br />\n當見到呢d野既時間(唔計殺你果種，講嚇你果種)<br />\n<br />\n一定嚇到仆街，但當你諗下侲件事之後想點<br />\n<br />\n成件事變到有d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n用電影情節做例: <br />\n<br />\n洗完面抬起頭塊鏡自己個樣變左鬼，一定嚇到仆街，叫完之後繼續望住塊鏡。都係果個鬼樣，跟住呢？點埋尾？你眼望我眼<br />\n<br />\n例2: 打開衣櫥見貞子類既鬼係入面，又係好撚驚嚇。之後佢繼續係我衣櫥度。。。跟住呢？佢去邊好？繼續喺入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nsharing 完。唔教人點唔驚鬼或點點點。只係覺得咁既情況好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申都係好驚鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44e9b73410bee0f5dd115252609f031cbc269c7c","tid":344024,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:36:17.000Z","msg":"成日見啲留言講自己撞嘢經歷<br />\n見到... 喺窗口... 咁跟住呢? 咁跟住呢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d091753c59533e91f01de4673b0364e12143fd5","tid":344024,"uid":6443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T04:17:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日見啲留言講自己撞嘢經歷<br />\n見到... 喺窗口... 咁跟住呢? 咁跟住呢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n跟住佢會繼續係窗出面....唔知等到幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n淩空係窗出面..."},{"pid":"4eccb6a1cee50b688ee0e6dadf51b6d6ec08949e","tid":344024,"uid":6268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T04:33:12.000Z","msg":"跟住咪係你眼前消失<br />\n再耐唔耐又走出黎嚇你囉"}]}